<p>
   13. Virginia Tech
<p>
   14. Miami
<p>
   15. Northwestern
<p>
   16. Washington
<p>
   17. Kansas State
<p>
   18. Iowa
<p>
   19. Notre Dame
<p>
   20. Michigan
<p>
   21. Syracuse
<p>
   22. Wyoming
<p>
   23. Texas
<p>
   24. Auburn
<p>
   25. Army.
<p>
   Others receiving votes: West Virginia, Navy, East Carolina,
Southern Mississippi, Stanford, Wisconsin, San Diego State,
Virginia.
