<PREAMBLE>
 &UR; BC-RUSSIA-NO-MORALS-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; RUSSIA IS ADRIFT WITH NO MORAL COMPASS &LR;  &QL; 
</PREAMBLE>
<TEXT>
<p>
    &UR; (For purchase information  &MD;  the rates are not prohibitive --
contact one of these New York Times Syndicate sales
representatives: &LR; 
