310-996-0089. &LR; 
 &UR; By DAVID REMNICK &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; c.1997 Foreign Affairs Magazine &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QC; 
<p>
   PLEASE NOTE: This article has been transmitted twice, into the
``i'' international and ``k'' commentary files.
