<PREAMBLE>
 &UR; BC-STATES-BUDGET &QL;  THIS IS THE STATES NEWS SERVICE BUDGET FOR
JANUARY 22, 1997
</PREAMBLE>
<TEXT>
<p>
   IF YOU HAVE ANY QUESTIONS, PLEASE CALL US AT (202) 628-3100
