<PREAMBLE>
 &UR; BC-SOC-BURN-PEINADO-BLOOM &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; MAJOR LEAGUE SOCCER'S DALLAS BURN SIGN DANIEL PEINADO &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (For use by New York Times News Service clients) &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; By Michael Buteau &LR;  &QC; 
