<p>
   CATEGORY 6202/64033.2  &MD;  O.J. SIMPSON CIVIL TRIAL  &MD;  Attorneys for
the plaintiffs are expected to wind up their closing arguments
today, accusing O.J. Simpson of being responsible for the deaths of
Nicole Brown Simpson and Ronald Goldman. Following their remarks,
the defense in the case will begin its closing arguments. Cityline
will update this category AS NEW INFORMATION IS AVAILABLE.
