 &UR; BC-TEXAS-STOCKS-CLOSE-REPEAT-BLOOM &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; TEXAS STOCKS: WEAK OILFIELD-SERVICE STOCKS DRAG INDEX LOWER &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (For use by New York Times News Service clients) &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; By Daniel Fisher &LR;  &QC; 
