<PREAMBLE>
 &UR; BC-WEATHER-MAP-NYT &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; WEATHER &LR;  &QL; 
(Editors: The following text accompanies the weather map for
Thursday, Jan. 23, 1997, sent to computer graphics clients of The
New York Times News Service. For information call: 212-556-4204.) &QL; 
(bl) &QL; 
 &UR; c.1997 N.Y. Times News Service &LR;  &QL; 
