   -- CareMatrix Corporation (CMD US) was rated ``buy'' in new
coverage by analyst Ray Lewis at NatWest Securities Corp. The
12-month price target is $22 per share.
<p>
   -- Suburban Propane Partners Lp (SPH US) was downgraded to
``neutral''
from ``outperform'' by analysts Yves C. Siegel and Daniel L. Tulis
at Smith
Barney.
<p>
