from
``neutral'' by analyst David K. Dwyer at Smith Barney.
<p>
   -- Pt Bank Danamon (BDMN IJ) was reinstated medium-term
``accumulate''
by analyst at Merrill Lynch &AMP; Co. The previous rating was
''neutral.'' The
<p>
