 &UR; BC-JAPAN-PAPERS-BLOOM &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; TOP STORIES FROM MAJOR JAPANESE MORNING NEWSPAPERS, JAN. 23 &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (For use by New York Times News Service clients) &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; By Tak Kumakura &LR;  &QC; 
