 &UR; BC-COLONY-TRUMP-BLOOM &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; COLONY TO RECEIVE PREFERRED EQUITY FOR TRUMP'S CASTLE STAKE &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (For use by New York Times News Service clients) &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; By John Gorham &LR;  &QC; 
