<PREAMBLE>
 &UR; BC-JDS-FITEL-SHARES-UPDATE1-BLOOM &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; JDS FITEL'S SHARES RISE ON FISCAL 2ND-QTR PROFIT (UPDATE1) &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (For use by New York Times News Service clients) &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; By Mark Evans &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; c.1997 Bloomberg News &LR;  &QC; 
