<PREAMBLE>
 &UR; BC-RJR-SORENSEN-CORRECT-BLOOM &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; R.J. REYNOLDS HEAD OF MARKETING, SORENSEN, LEAVES (CORRECT) &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (For use by New York Times News Service clients) &LR;  &QC; 
