<p>
   (NYT14) NEW YORK -- Jan. 22, 1997 -- NY-RUSSIA-LEBED-CLR, 1-22
-- Alexander Lebed, right, is greeted by Donald Trump at his Fifth
Avenue office. Lebed is in New York to court investors, but his
visit to the United States has been widely viewed as an attempt to
win the support of American businessmen and to portray himself as
